## Tool / session artifacts
# Ignore .claude/ contents (worktrees, settings.local.json, etc.) but allow
# the shared project-scope plugin config. Negation only works when the parent
# dir isn't excluded — see https://git-scm.com/docs/gitignore (#PATTERN FORMAT).
.claude/*
!/.claude/settings.json
.superpowers/
*.binlog
screenshot_*.png
TestApp_backup.zip
_WinUITest/
